data.description: BEAUTIFUL 2 BED/2 BATH APARTMENT (WATCH THE VIRTUAL VIDEO), WITH SPLIT FLOOR PLAN WITH 2 ENTRANCES!!! UNIT HAS AMAZING CITY AND BAY VIEWS. FLOOR TO CEILING WINDOWS IN ALL AREAS. LAMINATED AND TILE FLOORS, BRIGHT UNIT WITH BALCONY IN EVERY ROOM, THERE IS ALSO WASHER AND DRYER INSIDE THE UNIT. THIS WATERFRONT CONDO OFFERS A VARIETY OF AMENITIES ON-SITE: MINI MARKET, COFFEE SHOP, SWIMMING POOL, GYM, BEAUTY PARLOR, RESTAURANT, AND MARINA. THE GRANDVIEW PALACE IS CENTRALLY LOCATED AND MINUTES FROM MIAMI BEACH, NEAR NORMANDY ISLES PARK, LA GORCE COUNTRY CLUB, AND LINCOLN ROAD MALL. POOL UNDERGOING MAINTENANCE, UNIT IS RENTED FOR $3,500 UNTIL AUGUST 2024, UNIT COMES WITH 2 PARKING SPACES, BUILDING VERY WELL ESTABLISHED, GREAT RESERVES, NO SPECIAL ASSESMENTS.
